text: Martadoris divae is a species of sea slug, a dorid nudibranch, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Polyceridae.MolluscaBase (2018). Martadoris divae (Er. Marcus, 1987). Accessed through: World Register of Marine Species on 2018-09-09. ==Distribution== This species was described from Arraial do Cabo, Cabo Frio, Brazil. ==References== Category:Polyceridae Category:Gastropods described in 1958
title: Martadoris divae
